BalmCo

Pain Medication: Regimagined

BalmCo Is A Platform Dedicated To Revolutionizing The World Of Pain Medication By Increasing Access To Compounded Topical Medications For All

Why Choose BalmCo?

BalmCo was created to provide patients around the US with access to powerful pain medications without dangerous side effects at affordable prices.

Patient Benefits

  • Fraction of the price of traditional pain medications
  • Avoid the side effects of other pain medications
  • Avoid long-term increases on insurance premiums
  • Shipped directly to your home for free

Doctor Benefits

  • Access to an easy to use platform for ordering compound pain medications.
  • No prior authorizations
  • Access to a whole new set of treatment options
  • Decreased financial burdens on healthcare system

How It Works

1

First, your doctor will evaluate you in the doctors office.

2

Your doctor will then select a specific compounded topical pain medication suited to your needs.

3

An email will be sent for you provide billing and shipping information, and your medication will be delivered directly to you.
